      <h2>Donate to Angel’s Garden Foundation</h2>
      <p>
        Your generosity plants seeds that grow into strong futures. Every gift—large or small—helps us serve
        underserved youth and families in need.
      </p>

      <h3>Why Give?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide scholarships for underserved students.</li>
        <li>Support Christian mentorship and leadership programs.</li>
        <li>Help families in crisis receive emergency assistance.</li>
        <li>Strengthen the next generation of responsible leaders.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Ways to Give</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>One‑time donation.</li>
        <li>Monthly giving as an ongoing partner.</li>
        <li>Sponsor a student’s education and mentoring.</li>
        <li>Support the emergency relief fund for families in crisis.</li>
      </ul>

